__ Cantrip: Health ___________________________ Cost: 20 _____________________

Use:  cantrip health                           Material Component: none
Use:  C health 

The cantrip health is a minor magic of the spheres of healing/abjuration.
When traced, the three fingered rune of health will keep the caster from
catching a disease.  This cantrip is an effective cure for seasickness!

NOTE: This cantrip will *not* protect you from a disease that you already
have!
